","history":"/rest/api/content/2743992321/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2743992321/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2743992321/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2743992321","tinyui":"/x/AQCOow","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2743992321","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2743992321/DBA+Migration+to+Tpago","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2743992321"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"bb95d958-acaa-40d6-9cf8-d8224fc83092\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 145.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 529.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 86.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p /></th><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Hrs.</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>Payment Link Portal</p></td><td><p>Vista para cargar la planilla de migraci&oacute;n</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Cambio en lista de suscriptores para listar la lista completa de los mismos y no separado por link (preguntar si esto va junto con dba)</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Analizar todo el portal para validar que el usuario sea un &ldquo;anonymous_subscriber&rdquo; y no hacer llamados a auth, ademas de verificar datos que se usen de ese usuario.</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>Payment Link Service</p></td><td><p>Agregar flag en el modelo de subscriber para diferenciar los subs de la migraci&oacute;n vs los subs de las suscripciones normales. &ldquo;anonymous_subscriber&rdquo; como idea. (subs sin user_id)</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Analizar proceso de suscriptores para validar que el usuario sea un &ldquo;anonymous_subscriber&rdquo; y no hacer llamados a auth, ademas de verificar datos que se usen de ese usuario.</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Procesador de planilla para crear suscripci&oacute;n, subs y medios de pago. Agregar comunicaci&oacute;n con nuevo servicio de external-services para datos de tarjeta</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p /></td><td><p>Modificar registro de tarjetas de d&eacute;bito/credito para actualizar tarjetas anteriormente catastradas como &ldquo;an&oacute;nimas&rdquo; y agregar datos faltantes</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>External Services</p></td><td><p>Agregar comunicaci&oacute;n con servicio externo para obtener por n&uacute;mero de contrato, comercio y sucursal los datos de la tarjeta</p></td><td><p /></td></tr></tbody></table><h2>Comentarios</h2><ul><li><p>El cambio en la lista de suscriptores, va junto con esta iniciativa? O se va a llevar por separado?</p></li></ul><p />","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2744025089"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":160500662},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2744025089/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2744025089/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2744025089/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2744025089/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2744025089","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2744025089/DBA+Migration+to+Tpago+-+Tasking+and+Estimation","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2744025089","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2744025089","tinyui":"/x/AYCOow","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}